<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="394" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1437,1004,1283]" pageId="13" pageNumber="394">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,297,1004,1030]" pageId="13" pageNumber="394">Description.</emphasis>
Face pale yellow with dark spots (
<figureCitation box="[693,779,1004,1030]" captionStart="FIGURES 29–47" captionStartId="11.[151,264,1997,2021]" captionTargetBox="[176,1408,535,1967]" captionTargetId="figure-133@11.[174,1412,525,1974]" captionTargetPageId="11" captionText="FIGURES 29–47. Macropsis spp., lateral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4404167" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4404167/files/figure.png" pageId="13" pageNumber="394">Fig. 40</figureCitation>
). Pronotum yellowish brown with darker median area and back margin and with dark spots on fore margin behind eyes. Scutellum pale yellow. Forewings brown with darker mesonotal margins. Male darker than female.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1437,1004,1283]" box="[199,942,1112,1139]" pageId="13" pageNumber="394">
Body length (including tegmina): 
<specimenCount box="[580,603,1113,1139]" pageId="13" pageNumber="394" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
, 4.0– 
<quantity box="[665,753,1112,1139]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.4" pageId="13" pageNumber="394" unit="mm" value="4.4">4.4 mm</quantity>
; 
<specimenCount box="[765,786,1113,1139]" pageId="13" pageNumber="394" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
, 4.5–5.0 mm.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
